	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-title": "方針與指引",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-body": "請查看維基百科上的可接受與預期內容。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-mobile-summary": "借鑒最佳實踐，打造自由可靠的百科全書。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-title": "中立的觀點",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-definition": "內容必須以公平、恰當、公正來呈現重要觀點。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-example-1": "紐約洋基隊是歷史上最偉大的棒球隊。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-answer-1-label": "不中立：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-answer-1-text": "這種觀點缺乏可靠來源的支持。您可以改寫成：「紐約洋基隊贏過26次世界大賽冠軍—幾乎是其他任何球隊的三倍。」",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-example-2": "威廉·莎士比亞被廣泛認為是英語界最偉大的作家之一。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-answer-2-label": "中立：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-answer-2-text": "這是恰當的名聲定義。有效性在於許多可靠來源都指出莎士比亞享有此名聲。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-title": "沒有原創研究",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-definition": "條目應透過已發表的來源總結，不應包含使用者自己的見解或知識。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-example-1": "今年11月的氣溫比去年高。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-answer-1-label": "包含原創研究：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-answer-1-text": "該說法沒有任何可靠的相關來源資料支持。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-example-2": "聽音樂的人會感到壓力減少[可靠來源]。壓力減少與壽命延長有關[可靠來源]。因此，聽音樂有助於延長壽命。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-answer-2-label": "包含原創研究：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-answer-2-text": "不應將多個來源資料彙整後，總結或暗示出任何其中之一來源並未明確提出的結論。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-title": "可查證性",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-definition": "新增內容應包含引用，提供出資訊來源。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-example-1": "突發新聞。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-1-label": "原則上不接受：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-1-text": "突發新聞報導往往包含不準確之處。最好在某個事件發生一兩天後，再將詳情加入維基百科。這樣可以給記者更多時間收集資訊，也讓調查機構有時間發布官方聲明。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-example-2": "來自社群媒體貼文的內容。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-2-label": "不可靠：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-2-text": "來自社群媒體的內容通常不被接受。但如果是由業內知名專家發布，則可以考慮採用。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-example-3": "內容來自有權威性的學術期刊或書籍。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-3-label": "可靠：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-3-text": "內容應來自於可靠、獨立、以事實查核與準確性著稱的發表來源。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-title": "假定善意",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-definition": "請記住，大多數使用者都是在努力改善維基百科，而不是故意降低品質。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-example-1": "「我真不敢相信你竟然因為編輯格式錯誤而搞砸了我的頁面，給我停止編輯維基百科！」",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-answer-1-label": "非假定善意：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-answer-1-text": "當有編者犯錯時，請不要指責他們是惡意行事。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-example-2": "「我注意到閣下編輯後的格式有點問題。我已經幫閣下修改好了，另外這個說明頁面可以幫助您下一次編輯。」",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-answer-2-label": "假定善意：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-answer-2-text": "除非有明顯的惡意行為證據，否則應該互相幫助以提高條目品質。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-examples-button": "範例",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-examples-progress": "$1/$2",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-examples-header": "範例：$1",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-next-button": "下一個",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-previous-button": "上一個",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-got-it-button": "了解"
}
